msgstr "For detailed comparison, see :doc:`6-trader-snapshot-gate`."

#: ../../source/live_trading/4-broker-adapter-and-integration.md:90
msgid ""
"提交前订单结构与回报字段均经契约校验，格式不对时会尽早报错，避免「脏数据"
"进账本」。"
msgstr ""
"Before submission, the order structure and reward fields are validated "
"under contract. If the format is incorrect, an error will be reported as "
"soon as possible to avoid \"dirty data entering the ledger\"."

#: ../../source/live_trading/4-broker-adapter-and-integration.md:92
msgid "4. 扩展新 Broker 类型"
msgstr "4. Expand the Broker type"

#: ../../source/live_trading/4-broker-adapter-and-integration.md:94
msgid "注册工厂（示例）："
msgstr "Register a factory (example):"

#: ../../source/live_trading/4-broker-adapter-and-integration.md:103
msgid ""
"**CLI `sync`（别名 `pull-state`）**：当前为**预留**，执行会打印 "
"`[NOT_IMPLEMENTED] ...`，表示真实「从券商拉状态」尚未实现；对接 QMT 后将"
"替换为可用实现。"
msgstr ""
"**CLI `sync` (alias `pull-state`):** Currently **reserved**, execution "
"will print `[NOT_IMPLEMENTED] ...`, indicating that the actual \"pull "
"state from brokerage\" has not yet been implemented; it will be replaced "
"with an available implementation after integration with QMT."

#: ../../source/live_trading/4-broker-adapter-and-integration.md:105
msgid "5. 边界行为（接入时请注意）"
msgstr "5. Boundary behavior (please pay attention during access)"

#: ../../source/live_trading/4-broker-adapter-and-integration.md:107
msgid ""
"未 `connect` 就 `submit` / `poll_fills`：应得到明确错误，而非静默失败"
msgstr ""
"Submitting or polling without connecting should result in an explicit "
"error, not a silent failure."

#: ../../source/live_trading/4-broker-adapter-and-integration.md:108
msgid "`cancel` 未知委托号：应稳定返回「未撤成」"
msgstr ""
"`cancel` Unknown delegation number: Should consistently return "
"\"Cancelled\"."

#: ../../source/live_trading/4-broker-adapter-and-integration.md:109
msgid "`poll_fills` 超时：应返回空列表，而非脏数据"
msgstr ""
"`poll_fills` timeout: An empty list should be returned, not dirty data."

#: ../../source/live_trading/4-broker-adapter-and-integration.md:110
msgid "simulator 上 **`connect` 不代表真实券商会话**，仅表示适配层可受理"
msgstr ""
"On the simulator, **`connect` does not represent a real brokerage "
"session; it only indicates that the adaptation layer can handle it."

